videos.description: Baylor QB Zach Smith's pass is intercepted by DeShon Elliott and returned for a 43-yard touchdown to give Texas the early lead.
videos.headline: Texas scores off interception

videos.description: Shane Buechele finds on open Lil'Jordan Humphrey in the end zone for a 15-yard touchdown to increase Texas's lead over Baylor.
videos.headline: Texas pads lead with TD

videos.description: With his team behind him, John Lovett pushes his way into the end zone for a 2-yard touchdown to chip away at Texas' lead.
videos.headline: Lovett muscles his way into the end zone

videos.description: Texas quarterback Shane Buechele takes the ball into his own hands and rushes 28 yards into the end zone for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Buechele goes the distance for TD

videos.description: Charles Omenihu strips John Lovett and the ball is recovered by Texas' John Bonney for a possession that would lead to a field goal.
videos.headline: Texas defense has third takeaway of the game

videos.description: Shane Buechele's pass is intercepted by Baylor's Grayland Arnold in the end zone and returned 20 yards.
videos.headline: Texas gets intercepted in the end zone

videos.description: On the first play of the fourth quarter, Toneil Carter burst into the end zone on a 19-yard run to cushion Texas' lead over Baylor.
videos.headline: Texas scores first in the 4th quarter
